'''Niyoon''' ([[ingiriis]]: Neon) astaanta ([[Ne]]) waa [[curiye]] kimiko oo leh lambar [[atom]] [[toban]] ah. 
Curiyaha Niyoon waa [[neef]] ka tirsan [[guruubka 18]]aad ee neefaha loo yaqaano [[Neefaha Gobta]] (Noble Gases). 

Neefta Niyoon waa mid bilaa midab ah, bilaa [[ur]] ah marka [[heerkul]]ku caadiga yahay, isla markaana leh labinlaab [[cuf]]ka [[hawo|hawada]] caadiga ah. 
Curiyahan Niyoon waxaa la helay [[sanad|sanadkii 1898]] ayaa waxay tahay [[neef]]ta afaraad ee ayadoo qalalan ku dhex jirta hawada, waxa ka horeeya [[Nitrojiin]]ta, [[Ogsajiin]]ta, [[Aargon]]ta iyo [[isku dhis]]ka [[Kaarboon|Kaarboob-labo-ogsaydh]] oo kali ah. 

Iskudhisyo ay Niyoontu ka mid tahay waxaa lagu isticmaala laydhka iyo laambadaha. 

Niyoon wuxuu dareereyaa -246.048 °C (-411 °F) wuxuuna ku qaboojiyaa heerkul kaliya 21/2° hoose.<ref>[https://www.britannica.com/science/neon-chemical-element Neon — Britannica]</ref>

